358bool IsValidPlatformTarget(Unit const* target)
359{
360 return target->GetExactDist2dSq(&CenterPosition) < 90.0f * 90.0f && target->GetPositionZ() > 840.0f && target->GetPositionZ() < 875.0f;
361}
362
363void SendPacketToPlayers(WorldPacket const* data, Unit* source)
364{
365 // Send packet to all players in The Frozen Throne
366 Map::PlayerList const& players = source->GetMap()->GetPlayers();
367 if (!players.IsEmpty())
368 for (Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = players.begin(); itr != players.end(); ++itr)
369 if (Player* player = itr->GetSource())
370 if (player->GetAreaId() == AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE)
371 player->GetSession()->SendPacket(data);
372}
373
374struct ShadowTrapLKTargetSelector
375{
376public:
377 ShadowTrapLKTargetSelector(Creature* source, bool playerOnly = true, bool reqLOS = false, float maxDist = 0.0f) : _source(source), _playerOnly(playerOnly), _reqLOS(reqLOS), _maxDist(maxDist) { }
378 bool operator()(Unit const* target) const
379 {
380 if (!target)
381 return false;
382 if (!target->IsAlive())
383 return false;
384 if (_playerOnly && target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
385 return false;
386 if (_maxDist && _source->GetExactDist(target) > _maxDist)
387 return false;
388 if (_reqLOS && !_source->IsWithinLOSInMap(target))
389 return false;
390 return true;
391 }
392
393private:
394 Creature const* _source;
395 bool _playerOnly;
396 bool _reqLOS;
397 float _maxDist;
398};
399
400struct NonTankLKTargetSelector
401{
402public:
403 NonTankLKTargetSelector(Creature* source, bool playerOnly = true, bool reqLOS = false, float maxDist = 0.0f, uint32 exclude1 = 0, uint32 exclude2 = 0) : _source(source), _playerOnly(playerOnly), _reqLOS(reqLOS), _maxDist(maxDist), _exclude1(exclude1), _exclude2(exclude2) { }
404 bool operator()(Unit const* target) const
405 {
406 if (!target)
407 return false;
408 if (!target->IsAlive())
409 return false;
410 if (_playerOnly && target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
411 return false;
412 if (target == _source->GetVictim())
413 return false;
414 if (target->HasAura(SPELL_BOSS_HITTIN_YA_AURA))
415 return false;
416 if (_maxDist && _source->GetExactDist(target) > _maxDist)
417 return false;
418 if ((_exclude1 && target->HasAura(_exclude1)) || (_exclude2 && target->HasAura(_exclude2)))
419 return false;
420 if (_reqLOS && !_source->IsWithinLOSInMap(target))
421 return false;
422 return true;
423 }
424
425private:
426 Creature const* _source;
427 bool _playerOnly;
428 bool _reqLOS;
429 float _maxDist;
430 uint32 _exclude1;
431 uint32 _exclude2;
432};
433
434struct DefileTargetSelector
435{
436public:
437 DefileTargetSelector(Creature* source) : _source(source) { }
438 bool operator()(Unit const* target) const
439 {
440 if (!target)
441 return false;
442 if (!target->IsAlive())
443 return false;
444 if (target->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER)
445 return false;
446 if (_source->GetExactDist(target) > 100.0f)
447 return false;
448 if (target->HasAura(SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_VALKYR) || target->HasAura(SPELL_VALKYR_TARGET_SEARCH))
449 return false;
450 if (!_source->IsWithinLOSInMap(target))
451 return false;
452 return true;
453 }
454
455private:
456 Creature const* _source;
457};
458
459class FrozenThroneResetWorker
460{
461public:
462 FrozenThroneResetWorker() { }
463
464 bool operator()(GameObject* go)
465 {
466 switch (go->GetEntry())
467 {
468 case GO_ARTHAS_PLATFORM:
469 go->SetDestructibleState(GO_DESTRUCTIBLE_INTACT, nullptr, true);
470 break;
471 case GO_DOODAD_ICECROWN_THRONEFROSTYWIND01:
472 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE);
473 break;
474 case GO_DOODAD_ICECROWN_THRONEFROSTYEDGE01:
475 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_READY);
476 break;
477 case GO_DOODAD_ICECROWN_SNOWEDGEWARNING01:
478 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_READY);
479 break;
480 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING02:
481 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING01:
482 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING03:
483 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING04:
484 go->ResetDoorOrButton();
485 break;
486 default:
487 break;
488 }
489
490 return false;
491 }
492};
493
494class StartMovementEvent : public BasicEvent
495{
496public:
497 StartMovementEvent(Creature* summoner, Creature* owner) : _summoner(summoner), _owner(owner) {}
498
499 bool Execute(uint64 /*time*/, uint32 /*diff*/) override
500 {
501 _owner->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
502 if (!_owner->GetThreatMgr().isThreatListEmpty())
503 if (Unit* target = _owner->SelectVictim())
504 _owner->AI()->AttackStart(target);
505 if (!_owner->GetVictim())
506 if (Unit* target = _summoner->AI()->SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, NonTankLKTargetSelector(_summoner)))
507 _owner->AI()->AttackStart(target);
508 _owner->AI()->DoZoneInCombat();
509 return true;
510 }
511
512private:
513 Creature* _summoner;
514 Creature* _owner;
515};
516
517class VileSpiritActivateEvent : public BasicEvent
518{
519public:
520 explicit VileSpiritActivateEvent(Creature* owner) : _owner(owner) {}
521
522 bool Execute(uint64 /*time*/, uint32 /*diff*/) override
523 {
524 _owner->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
525 _owner->CastSpell(_owner, SPELL_VILE_SPIRIT_MOVE_SEARCH, true);
526 _owner->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_VILE_SPIRIT_DAMAGE_SEARCH, true);
527 return true;
528 }
529
530private:
531 Creature* _owner;
532};
533
534class TriggerWickedSpirit : public BasicEvent
535{
536public:
537 explicit TriggerWickedSpirit(Creature* owner)
538 : _owner(owner), _counter(13)
539 {
540 }
541
542 bool Execute(uint64 /*time*/, uint32 /*diff*/) override
543 {
544 _owner->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_TRIGGER_VILE_SPIRIT_HEROIC, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1, nullptr, true);
545
546 if (--_counter)
547 {
548 _owner->m_Events.AddEvent(this, _owner->m_Events.CalculateTime(3000));
549 return false;
550 }
551
552 return true;
553 }
554
555private:
556 Creature* _owner;
557 uint32 _counter;
558};

560class LichKingDeathEvent : public BasicEvent
561{

564
565 bool Execute(uint64 /*eventTime*/, uint32 /*updateTime*/) override
566 {
567 _owner.RemoveAllAuras();

569 return true;
570 }
571
572private:
573 Creature& _owner;
574};

591class NecroticPlagueTargetCheck
592{
593public:
594 NecroticPlagueTargetCheck(Unit const* obj, uint32 notAura1, uint32 notAura2) : _sourceObj(obj), _notAura1(notAura1), _notAura2(notAura2) {}
595
596 bool operator()(Unit* unit) const
597 {
598 if (!unit || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || unit == _sourceObj || _sourceObj->GetVictim() == unit || !unit->isTargetableForAttack())
599 return false;
600 if (unit->HasAura(SPELL_PLAGUE_AVOIDANCE) || unit->HasAura(SPELL_BOSS_HITTIN_YA_AURA) || unit->HasAura(_notAura1) || unit->HasAura(_notAura2))
601 return false;
602 if (!_sourceObj->IsWithinLOSInMap(unit))
603 return false;
604 return true;
605 }
606
607private:
608 Unit const* _sourceObj;
609 uint32 _notAura1;
610 uint32 _notAura2;
611};
612
613class HeightDifferenceCheck
614{
615public:
616 HeightDifferenceCheck(GameObject* go, float diff, bool reverse) : _baseObject(go), _difference(diff), _reverse(reverse) {}
617 bool operator()(WorldObject* unit) const { return (unit->GetPositionZ() - _baseObject->GetPositionZ() > _difference) != _reverse; }
618private:
619 GameObject* _baseObject;
620 float _difference;
621 bool _reverse;
622};

629 struct boss_the_lich_kingAI : public BossAI

631 boss_the_lich_kingAI(Creature* creature) : BossAI(creature, DATA_THE_LICH_KING)

633 me->AddAura(SPELL_EMOTE_SIT_NO_SHEATH, me);
634 me->SetImmuneToPC(true);

688 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR, 15000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);

692 if (IsHeroic())
693 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHADOW_TRAP, 15500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
694 }

704 Cell::VisitGridObjects(me, worker, 333.0f);
705

707 me->SetImmuneToPC(true);
708 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);

722 void KilledUnit(Unit* victim) override
723 {
724 if (victim->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && !me->IsInEvadeMode() && _phase != PHASE_OUTRO && _lastTalkTimeKill + 5 < GameTime::GetGameTime().count())
725 {

730
731 void DoAction(int32 action) override
732 {
733 switch (action)
734 {
735 case ACTION_RESTORE_LIGHT:
736 me->GetMap()->SetZoneOverrideLight(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, 0, 5s);
737 me->GetMap()->SetZoneWeather(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, WEATHER_STATE_FINE, 0.5f);
738 break;
739 case ACTION_START_ATTACK:
740 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_START_ATTACK, 5250);
741 break;
742 case ACTION_BREAK_FROSTMOURNE:
743 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_SUMMON_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE, true);
744 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_SUMMON_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE_2, false);
745 SetEquipmentSlots(false, EQUIP_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE);
746 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
747 tirion->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_BREAK_FROSTMOURNE);
748 break;
749 case ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK:
750 {
751 if (_phase == PHASE_FROSTMOURNE)
752 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_START_ATTACK, 1000);
753 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE);
754 summons.DoAction(ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK, pred);
755 if (!IsHeroic() && _phase != PHASE_OUTRO && me->IsInCombat() && _lastTalkTimeBuff + 5 <= GameTime::GetGameTime().count())
756 Talk(SAY_LK_FROSTMOURNE_ESCAPE);
757 }
758 break;
759 default:
760 break;
761 }
762 }
763
764 void DamageTaken(Unit* attacker, uint32& damage, DamageEffectType, SpellSchoolMask) override
765 {
766 if (!attacker || (_bFrostmournePhase && attacker->GetExactDistSq(495.708f, -2523.76f, 1049.95f) > 40.0f * 40.0f)) // frostmourne room, prevent exploiting (tele hack to get back and damage him)
767 {
768 damage = 0;
769 return;
770 }
771
772 if (_phase == PHASE_ONE && !HealthAbovePct(70) && !me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
773 {
774 _phase = PHASE_TRANSITION;
775 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
776 me->AttackStop();
777 events.CancelEventGroup(EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
778 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(false);
779 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_CENTER_1, CenterPosition);
780 return;
781 }
782
783 if (_phase == PHASE_TWO && !HealthAbovePct(40) && !me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
784 {
785 _phase = PHASE_TRANSITION;
786 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
787 me->AttackStop();
788 events.CancelEventGroup(EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
789 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(false);
790 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_CENTER_2, CenterPosition);
791 return;
792 }
793
794 if (_phase == PHASE_THREE && HealthBelowPct(10) && !me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
795 {
796 _phase = PHASE_OUTRO;
797 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE);
798 summons.DoAction(ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK, pred);
799 events.Reset();
800 summons.DespawnAll();
801 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
802 me->AttackStop();
803 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_FURY_OF_FROSTMOURNE);
804 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(true);
805 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_FURY_OF_FROSTMOURNE, false);
806 me->SetWalk(true);
807
808 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
809 tirion->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_OUTRO);
810 return;
811 }
812
813 if (_phase == PHASE_OUTRO)
814 {
815 if (!me->IsLevitating())
816 damage = me->GetHealth() > 1 ? 1 : 0;
817 else if (damage >= me->GetHealth()) // dying...
818 {
819 damage = me->GetHealth() - 1;
820 me->SetDisableGravity(false);
821 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFall();
822 if (Creature* frostmourne = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_FROSTMOURNE_TRIGGER, 50.0f))
823 frostmourne->DespawnOrUnsummon(1);
824 if (Creature* terenas = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_TERENAS_MENETHIL_OUTRO, 50.0f))
825 terenas->DespawnOrUnsummon(1);
826
827 me->m_Events.AddEvent(new LichKingDeathEvent(*me), me->m_Events.CalculateTime(2500)); // die after spinning anim is over, so death anim is visible
828 me->m_Events.AddEvent(new LichKingMovieEvent(*me), me->m_Events.CalculateTime(11500));
829 }
830
831 if (!_bFordringMustFallYell && me->GetHealth() < 500000)
832 {
833 _bFordringMustFallYell = true;
834 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
835 {
836 tirion->Yell("The Lich King must fall!", LANG_UNIVERSAL);
837 tirion->PlayDirectSound(17389);
838 }
839 }
840 }
841 else if (damage >= me->GetHealth())
842 damage = me->GetHealth() - 1;
843 }
844
845 void JustSummoned(Creature* summon) override
846 {
847 switch (summon->GetEntry())
848 {
849 case NPC_SHAMBLING_HORROR:
850 case NPC_DRUDGE_GHOUL:
851 summon->SetHomePosition(CenterPosition);
852 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_RISEN_WITCH_DOCTOR_SPAWN, true);
853 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
854 summon->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EMERGE);
855 summon->m_Events.AddEvent(new StartMovementEvent(me, summon), summon->m_Events.CalculateTime(5000));
856 break;
857 case NPC_RAGING_SPIRIT:
858 summon->SetHomePosition(CenterPosition);
859 break;
860 case NPC_VILE_SPIRIT:
861 {
862 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
863 summon->GetMotionMaster()->MoveRandom(10.0f);
864 if (_phase == PHASE_THREE)
865 summon->m_Events.AddEvent(new VileSpiritActivateEvent(summon), summon->m_Events.CalculateTime(15000));
866 break;
867 }
868 case NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE:
869 summons.Summon(summon);
870 return;
871 case NPC_DEFILE:
872 case NPC_SHADOW_TRAP_TRIGGER:
873 summon->m_positionZ = 840.86f;
874 summon->UpdatePosition(summon->GetPositionX(), summon->GetPositionY(), summon->GetPositionZ(), summon->GetOrientation(), true);
875 summon->StopMovingOnCurrentPos();
876 break;
877 case NPC_VALKYR_SHADOWGUARD:
878 if (_phase == PHASE_THREE || events.GetNextEventTime(EVENT_QUAKE_2))
879 summon->DespawnOrUnsummon(1);
880 break;
881 default:
882 break;
883 }
884
885 BossAI::JustSummoned(summon);
886 }
887
888 void SummonedCreatureDies(Creature* summon, Unit*) override
889 {
890 switch (summon->GetEntry())
891 {
892 case NPC_SHAMBLING_HORROR:
893 case NPC_DRUDGE_GHOUL:
894 case NPC_ICE_SPHERE:
895 case NPC_VALKYR_SHADOWGUARD:
896 case NPC_RAGING_SPIRIT:
897 case NPC_VILE_SPIRIT:
898 summon->ToTempSummon()->SetTimer(5000);
899 summon->ToTempSummon()->SetTempSummonType(TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN);
900 break;
901 default:
902 break;
903 }
904 }

937 //events.DelayEvents(62500, EVENT_GROUP_BERSERK); // delay berserk timer, its not ticking during phase transitions, 15mins on movies
938 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_QUAKE, 62500);
939 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, 3500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
940 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, 8000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
941 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT, 4000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
942 break;

946 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
947 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_REMORSELESS_WINTER_2, false);
948 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_VALKYR_SHADOWGUARD);
949 //events.DelayEvents(62500, EVENT_GROUP_BERSERK); // delay berserk timer, its not ticking during phase transitions, 15 mins on movies
950 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_QUAKE_2, 62500);
951 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, 3500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
952 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, 8000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
953 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT, 4000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
954 break;
955 default:
956 break;

959
960 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
961 {
962 if (_phase == PHASE_NONE)
963 return;
964
965 // check phase first to prevent updating victim and entering evade mode when not wanted
966 if (!((1 << _phase) & PHASE_MASK_NO_VICTIM))
967 if (!UpdateVictim())
968 return;
969
970 // handle falling players so they don't fall infinitely
971 if (_positionCheckTimer <= diff)
972 {
973 _positionCheckTimer = 5000;
974 Map::PlayerList const& players = me->GetMap()->GetPlayers();
975 if (!players.IsEmpty())
976 for (Map::PlayerList::const_iterator itr = players.begin(); itr != players.end(); ++itr)
977 if (Player* player = itr->GetSource())
978 if (player->GetPositionZ() < 700.0f)
979 Unit::Kill(me, player);
980 }
981 else
982 _positionCheckTimer -= diff;
983
984 events.Update(diff);
985
986 // during Remorseless Winter phases The Lich King is channeling a spell, but we must continue casting other spells
987 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING) && !((1 << _phase) & PHASE_MASK_NO_CAST_CHECK))
988 return;
989
990 switch (events.ExecuteEvent())
991 {
992 case EVENT_BERSERK:
993 Talk(SAY_LK_BERSERK);
994 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_BERSERK2, true);
995 break;
996 case EVENT_START_ATTACK:
997 me->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
998 if (_phase == PHASE_FROSTMOURNE)
999 {
1000 _bFrostmournePhase = false;
1001 _phase = PHASE_THREE;
1002 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 0, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1003 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, urand(7000, 12000), EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1004
1005 for (SummonList::iterator i = summons.begin(); i != summons.end(); ++i)
1006 if (Creature* summon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, *i))
1007 if (summon->GetEntry() == NPC_RAGING_SPIRIT)
1008 summon->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
1009 }
1010 break;
1011 case EVENT_QUAKE:
1012 _phase = PHASE_TWO;
1013 events.CancelEventGroup(EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1014 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INFEST, 14000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1015 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR, 20000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1016 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, 40000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1017 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 38000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1018
1019 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(false);
1020 me->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING);
1021 me->SetFacingTo(0.0f);
1022 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_QUAKE, false);
1023 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1024 Talk(SAY_LK_QUAKE);
1025 break;
1026 case EVENT_QUAKE_2:
1027 _phase = PHASE_THREE;
1028 events.CancelEventGroup(EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1029 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, 40000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1030 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 38000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1031 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VILE_SPIRITS, 20000, EVENT_GROUP_VILE_SPIRITS);
1032 events.ScheduleEvent(IsHeroic() ? EVENT_HARVEST_SOULS : EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL, 14000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1033
1034 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(false);
1035 me->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING);
1036 me->SetFacingTo(0.0f);
1037 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_QUAKE, false);
1038 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1039 Talk(SAY_LK_QUAKE);
1040 break;
1041
1042 // ABILITIES:
1043 case EVENT_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR:
1044 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR, false);
1045 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1046 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR, 60000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1047 break;
1048 case EVENT_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOUL:
1049 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOULS, false);
1050 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOUL, 30000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1051 break;
1052 case EVENT_INFEST:
1053 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_INFEST, false);
1054 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INFEST, 22500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1055 break;
1056 case EVENT_NECROTIC_PLAGUE:
1057 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, NecroticPlagueTargetCheck(me, NECROTIC_PLAGUE_LK, NECROTIC_PLAGUE_PLR)))
1058 {
1059 Talk(EMOTE_NECROTIC_PLAGUE_WARNING, target);
1060 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, false);
1061 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, urand(30000, 31000), EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1062 }
1063 else
1064 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, 5000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1065 break;
1066 case EVENT_SHADOW_TRAP:
1067 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, ShadowTrapLKTargetSelector(me, true, true, 100.0f)))
1068 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_SHADOW_TRAP, false);
1069 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHADOW_TRAP, 15500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1070 break;
1071 case EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING:
1072 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, 0.0f, true))
1073 {
1074 //events.DelayEventsToMax(500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1075 me->SetFacingTo(me->GetAngle(target));
1076 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, false);
1077 }
1078 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, (IsHeroic() ? urand(1250, 1750) : urand(1750, 2250)), EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1079 break;
1080 case EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE:
1081 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, false);
1082 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, 7500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1083 break;
1084 case EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT:
1085 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, 100.0f, true))
1086 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_RAGING_SPIRIT, false);
1087 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT, (!HealthAbovePct(40) ? 15000 : 20000), EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1088 break;
1089 case EVENT_DEFILE:
1090 {
1091 uint32 evTime = events.GetNextEventTime(EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR);
1092 // if defile (cast time 2sec) is less than 3 before valkyr appears
1093 // we've to decide
1094 if (evTime && (events.GetTimer() > evTime || evTime - events.GetTimer() < 5000))
1095 {
1096 // if valkyr is less than 1.5 secs after defile (cast time 2 sec) then we've a sync issue, so
1097 // we need to cancel it (break) and schedule a defile to be casted 5 or 4 seconds after valkyr
1098 if (events.GetTimer() > evTime || evTime - events.GetTimer() < 3500)
1099 {
1100 uint32 t = events.GetTimer() > evTime ? 0 : evTime - events.GetTimer();
1101 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, t + (Is25ManRaid() ? 5000 : 4000), EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1102 break;
1103 }
1104
1105 // if valkyr is coming between 1.5 and 3 seconds after defile then we've to
1106 // delay valkyr just a bit
1107 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR, 5000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1108 }
1109
1110 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, DefileTargetSelector(me)))
1111 {
1112 Talk(EMOTE_DEFILE_WARNING);
1113 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_DEFILE, false);
1114 // defile has a fixed CD (from dbm) that can be variable only
1115 // if no target has been found at the moment (schedule after 1 second)
1116 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 32500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1117 }
1118 else
1119 {
1120 // be sure it happen trying each seconds if no target
1121 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 1000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1122 }
1123 }
1124 break;
1125 case EVENT_SOUL_REAPER:
1126 if (me->IsWithinMeleeRange(me->GetVictim()))
1127 {
1128 me->CastSpell(me->GetVictim(), SPELL_SOUL_REAPER, false);
1129 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, 30500, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1130 }
1131 else
1132 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, 1000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1133 break;
1134 case EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR:
1135 {
1136 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1137 Talk(SAY_LK_SUMMON_VALKYR);
1138 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SUMMON_VALKYR, false);
1139 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR, 45000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1140
1141 // schedule a defile (or reschedule it) if next defile event
1142 // doesn't exist ( now > next defile ) or defile is coming too soon
1143 uint32 minTime = (Is25ManRaid() ? 5000 : 4000);
1144 if (uint32 evTime = events.GetNextEventTime(EVENT_DEFILE))
1145 if (events.GetTimer() > evTime || evTime - events.GetTimer() < minTime)
1146 {
1147 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, minTime, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1148 }
1149 }
1150 break;
1151 case EVENT_VILE_SPIRITS:
1152 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1153 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_VILE_SPIRITS, false);
1154 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VILE_SPIRITS, 30000, EVENT_GROUP_VILE_SPIRITS);
1155 break;
1156 case EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL:
1157 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, NonTankLKTargetSelector(me, true, true, 55.0f)))
1158 {
1159 Talk(SAY_LK_HARVEST_SOUL);
1160 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL, false);
1161 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL, 75000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1162 }
1163 else
1164 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL, 10000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1165 break;
1166 case EVENT_HARVEST_SOULS:
1167 Talk(SAY_LK_HARVEST_SOUL);
1168 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_HARVEST_SOULS, false);
1169 _phase = PHASE_FROSTMOURNE;
1170 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1171 me->AttackStop();
1172 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_START_ATTACK, 55000);
1173 events.DelayEvents(52500, EVENT_GROUP_VILE_SPIRITS);
1174 events.CancelEvent(EVENT_DEFILE);
1175 events.CancelEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER);
1176 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_HEROIC, 6000, EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1177 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HARVEST_SOULS, urand(100000, 110000), EVENT_GROUP_ABILITIES);
1178
1179 for (SummonList::iterator i = summons.begin(); i != summons.end(); ++i)
1180 if (Creature* summon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, *i))
1181 {
1182 if (summon->GetEntry() == NPC_VILE_SPIRIT)
1183 {
1184 summon->m_Events.KillAllEvents(true);
1185 summon->m_Events.AddEvent(new VileSpiritActivateEvent(summon), summon->m_Events.CalculateTime(55000));
1186 summon->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(true);
1187 summon->StopMoving();
1188 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1189 summon->AttackStop();
1190 }
1191 else if (summon->GetEntry() == NPC_RAGING_SPIRIT)
1192 {
1193 summon->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(true);
1194 summon->StopMoving();
1195 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1196 summon->AttackStop();
1197 }
1198 }
1199 break;
1200 case EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_HEROIC:
1201 _bFrostmournePhase = true;
1202 if (TempSummon* terenas = me->GetMap()->SummonCreature(NPC_TERENAS_MENETHIL_FROSTMOURNE_H, TerenasSpawnHeroic, nullptr, 55000))
1203 {
1204 terenas->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_FROSTMOURNE_INTRO);
1205 if (Creature* spawner = terenas->FindNearestCreature(NPC_WORLD_TRIGGER_INFINITE_AOI, 100.0f, true))
1206 {
1207 spawner->CastSpell(spawner, SPELL_SUMMON_SPIRIT_BOMB_1, true); // summons bombs randomly
1208 spawner->CastSpell(spawner, SPELL_SUMMON_SPIRIT_BOMB_2, true); // summons bombs on players
1209 spawner->m_Events.AddEvent(new TriggerWickedSpirit(spawner), spawner->m_Events.CalculateTime(3000));
1210 terenas->SetImmuneToAll(true); // to avoid being healed by player trinket procs. terenas' health doesn't matter on heroic
1211 }
1212 }
1213 break;
1214
1215 default:
1216 break;
1217 }
1218
1219 if (!me->HasReactState(REACT_PASSIVE) && me->GetVictim() && me->IsWithinMeleeRange(me->GetVictim()) && me->GetMotionMaster()->GetCurrentMovementGeneratorType() != POINT_MOTION_TYPE && !me->IsWithinLOSInMap(me->GetVictim()))
1220 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveCharge(me->GetVictim()->GetPositionX(), me->GetVictim()->GetPositionY(), me->GetVictim()->GetPositionZ(), me->GetSpeed(MOVE_RUN), POINT_NONE);
1221
1222 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1223 }
1224
1225 uint32 GetData(uint32 type) const override
1226 {
1227 switch (type)
1228 {
1229 case DATA_PLAGUE_STACK:
1230 return _necroticPlagueStack;
1231 case DATA_VILE:
1232 return _vileSpiritExplosions;
1233 default:
1234 break;
1235 }
1236
1237 return 0;
1238 }
1239
1240 void SetData(uint32 type, uint32 value) override
1241 {
1242 switch (type)
1243 {
1244 case DATA_PLAGUE_STACK:
1245 _necroticPlagueStack = std::max(value, _necroticPlagueStack);
1246 break;
1247 case DATA_VILE:
1248 _vileSpiritExplosions += value;
1249 break;
1250 default:
1251 break;
1252 }
1253 }
1254
1255 void EnterEvadeMode(EvadeReason why) override
1256 {
1257 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE);
1258 summons.DoAction(ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK, pred);
1259 instance->SetBossState(DATA_THE_LICH_KING, FAIL);
1260 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_KILL_FROSTMOURNE_PLAYERS, true);
1261 BossAI::EnterEvadeMode(why);
1262 me->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
1263
1264 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
1265 tirion->AI()->EnterEvadeMode();
1266 }
1267 };
1268
1269 CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* creature) const override
1270 {
1271 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<boss_the_lich_kingAI>(creature);
1272 }
1273};

1365 {
1366 Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING));
1367 if (me->GetCreatureTemplate()->GossipMenuId == sender && !action && me->HasNpcFlag(UNIT_NPC_FLAG_GOSSIP) && theLichKing && !theLichKing->IsInEvadeMode())

1371 me->RemoveNpcFlag(UNIT_NPC_FLAG_GOSSIP);

1601 case EVENT_OUTRO_LK_TALK_7:
1602 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1603 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_OUTRO_7);
1604 break;
1605 case EVENT_OUTRO_LK_TALK_8:
1606 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1607 theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_OUTRO_8);
1608 break;
1609 case EVENT_OUTRO_FORDRING_TALK_1:
1610 Talk(SAY_TIRION_OUTRO_1);
1611 break;
1612 case EVENT_OUTRO_FORDRING_BLESS:
1613 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_LIGHTS_BLESSING, false);
1614 break;
1615 case EVENT_OUTRO_FORDRING_REMOVE_ICE:
1616 me->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_ICE_LOCK);
1617 SetEquipmentSlots(false, EQUIP_ASHBRINGER_GLOWING);
1618 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1619 {
1620 me->SetFacingToObject(lichKing);
1621 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_FINAL);
1622 }
1623 break;
1624 case EVENT_OUTRO_FORDRING_MOVE_1:
1625 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_TIRION_OUTRO, OutroPosition1);
1626 break;
1627 case EVENT_OUTRO_FORDRING_JUMP:
1628 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_JUMP, false);
1629 break;
1630
1631 default:
1632 break;
1633 }
1634
1635 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1636 }
1637
1638 void EnterEvadeMode(EvadeReason why) override
1639 {
1640 if (!me->IsAlive())
1641 return;
1642
1643 if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1644 if (theLichKing->IsInEvadeMode())
1645 {
1646 ScriptedAI::EnterEvadeMode(why);
1647 return;
1648 }
1649
1650 me->GetThreatMgr().ClearAllThreat();
1651 me->CombatStop(false);
1652 }
1653
1654 bool CanAIAttack(Unit const* target) const override
1655 {
1656 return target->GetEntry() == NPC_THE_LICH_KING;
1657 }
1658
1659 private:
1660 EventMap _events;
1661 InstanceScript* _instance;
1662 };
1663
1664 CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* creature) const override
1665 {
1666 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_tirion_fordringAI>(creature);
1667 }
1668};

1804class npc_shambling_horror_icc : public CreatureScript
1805{
1806public:
1807 npc_shambling_horror_icc() : CreatureScript("npc_shambling_horror_icc") { }
1808
1809 struct npc_shambling_horror_iccAI : public ScriptedAI
1810 {
1811 npc_shambling_horror_iccAI(Creature* creature) : ScriptedAI(creature)
1812 {
1813 _frenzied = false;
1814 }
1815
1816 EventMap _events;
1817 bool _frenzied;
1818
1819 void Reset() override
1820 {
1821 _events.Reset();
1822 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOCKWAVE, urand(20000, 25000));
1823 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ENRAGE, urand(11000, 14000));
1824 }
1825
1826 void DamageTaken(Unit*, uint32& damage, DamageEffectType, SpellSchoolMask) override
1827 {
1828 if (!_frenzied && IsHeroic() && me->HealthBelowPctDamaged(20, damage))
1829 {
1830 _frenzied = true;
1831 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_FRENZY, true);
1832 }
1833 }
1834
1835 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
1836 {
1837 if (!UpdateVictim())
1838 return;
1839
1840 _events.Update(diff);
1841
1842 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
1843 return;
1844
1845 switch (_events.ExecuteEvent())
1846 {
1847 case EVENT_SHOCKWAVE:
1848 me->CastSpell(me->GetVictim(), SPELL_SHOCKWAVE, false);
1849 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOCKWAVE, urand(20000, 25000));
1850 break;
1851 case EVENT_ENRAGE:
1852 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_ENRAGE, false);
1853 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_ENRAGE, urand(20000, 25000));
1854 break;
1855 default:
1856 break;
1857 }
1858
1859 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1860 }
1861
1862 bool CanAIAttack(Unit const* target) const override
1863 {
1864 return IsValidPlatformTarget(target) && !target->GetVehicle();
1865 }
1866 };
1867
1868 CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* creature) const override
1869 {
1870 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_shambling_horror_iccAI>(creature);
1871 }
1872};

1914class spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague : public SpellScriptLoader
1915{
1916public:
1917 spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague") { }
1918

1920 {

1924 {
1925 return ValidateSpellInfo({ SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE_JUMP });
1926 }
1927
1928 void OnRemove(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
1929 {
1930 bool dispel = false;
1931 switch (GetTargetApplication()->GetRemoveMode())
1932 {
1933 case AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL:
1934 dispel = true;
1935 case AURA_REMOVE_BY_EXPIRE:
1936 case AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEATH:
1937 break;
1938 default:
1939 return;
1940 }
1941
1942 CustomSpellValues values;
1943 if (dispel)
1944 values.AddSpellMod(SPELLVALUE_BASE_POINT1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL); // add as marker (spell has no effect 1)
1945 GetTarget()->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE_JUMP, values, nullptr, TRIGGERED_FULL_MASK, nullptr, nullptr, GetCasterGUID());
1946
1947 if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
1948 caster->CastSpell(caster, SPELL_PLAGUE_SIPHON, true);
1949 }
1950
1951 void Register() override
1952 {
1953 AfterEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript::OnRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
1954 }
1955 };

1963class spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_jump : public SpellScriptLoader
1964{
1965public:
1966 spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_jump() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_jump") { }
1967
1968 class spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_SpellScript : public SpellScript
1969 {
1970 PrepareSpellScript(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_SpellScript);
1971
1972 bool Load() override
1973 {
1974 _hadJumpingAura = false;
1975 _hadInitialAura = false;
1976 return true;
1977 }
1978
1979 void FilterTargets(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
1980 {
1981 targets.sort(Acore::ObjectDistanceOrderPred(GetCaster()));
1982 if (targets.size() <= 1)
1983 return;
1984
1985 targets.resize(1);
1986 }
1987
1988 void CheckAura(SpellMissInfo missInfo)
1989 {
1990 if (missInfo != SPELL_MISS_NONE)
1991 {
1992 return;
1993 }
1994
1995 if (GetHitUnit()->HasAura(GetSpellInfo()->Id))
1996 _hadJumpingAura = true;
1997 else if (uint32 spellId = sSpellMgr->GetSpellIdForDifficulty(SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, GetHitUnit()))
1998 if (GetHitUnit()->HasAura(spellId))
1999 _hadInitialAura = true;
2000 }
2001
2002 void AddMissingStack()
2003 {
2004 if (GetHitAura() && !_hadJumpingAura)
2005 {
2006 uint32 spellId = sSpellMgr->GetSpellIdForDifficulty(SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, GetHitUnit());
2007 if (GetSpellValue()->EffectBasePoints[EFFECT_1] != AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL || _hadInitialAura)
2008 GetHitAura()->ModStackAmount(1);
2009 if (_hadInitialAura)
2010 if (Aura* a = GetHitUnit()->GetAura(spellId))
2011 a->Remove(AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEFAULT);
2012 }
2013 }
2014
2015 void Register() override
2016 {
2017 OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_SpellScript::FilterTargets, EFFECT_0, TARGET_UNIT_SRC_AREA_ENTRY);
2018 BeforeHit += BeforeSpellHitFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_SpellScript::CheckAura);
2019 OnHit += SpellHitFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_SpellScript::AddMissingStack);
2020 }
2021
2022 bool _hadJumpingAura;
2023 bool _hadInitialAura;
2024 };
2025
2026 class spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript : public AuraScript
2027 {
2028 PrepareAuraScript(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript);
2029
2030 bool Load() override
2031 {
2032 _lastAmount = 0;
2033 return true;
2034 }
2035
2036 void OnApply(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2037 {
2038 if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
2039 if (caster->GetAI())
2040 caster->GetAI()->SetData(DATA_PLAGUE_STACK, GetStackAmount());
2041 }
2042
2043 void OnRemove(AuraEffect const* aurEff, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2044 {
2045 _lastAmount = aurEff->GetAmount();
2046 switch (GetTargetApplication()->GetRemoveMode())
2047 {
2048 case AURA_REMOVE_BY_EXPIRE:
2049 case AURA_REMOVE_BY_DEATH:
2050 break;
2051 default:
2052 return;
2053 }
2054
2055 CustomSpellValues values;
2056 values.AddSpellMod(SPELLVALUE_AURA_STACK, GetStackAmount());
2057 GetTarget()->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE_JUMP, values, nullptr, TRIGGERED_FULL_MASK, nullptr, nullptr, GetCasterGUID());
2058 if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
2059 caster->CastSpell(caster, SPELL_PLAGUE_SIPHON, true);
2060 }
2061
2062 void OnDispel(AuraEffect const* aurEff, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2063 {
2064 _lastAmount = aurEff->GetAmount();
2065 }
2066
2067 void AfterDispel(AuraEffect const* aurEff, AuraEffectHandleModes /*mode*/)
2068 {
2069 // this means the stack increased so don't process as if dispelled
2070 if (aurEff->GetAmount() > _lastAmount)
2071 return;
2072
2073 CustomSpellValues values;
2074 values.AddSpellMod(SPELLVALUE_AURA_STACK, GetStackAmount());
2075 values.AddSpellMod(SPELLVALUE_BASE_POINT1, AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL); // add as marker (spell has no effect 1)
2076 GetTarget()->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE_JUMP, values, nullptr, TRIGGERED_FULL_MASK, nullptr, nullptr, GetCasterGUID());
2077 if (Unit* caster = GetCaster())
2078 caster->CastSpell(caster, SPELL_PLAGUE_SIPHON, true);
2079
2080 Remove(AURA_REMOVE_BY_ENEMY_SPELL);
2081 }
2082
2083 void Register() override
2084 {
2085 OnEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript::OnApply, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL_OR_REAPPLY_MASK);
2086 AfterEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript::OnRemove, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAL);
2087 AfterEffectRemove += AuraEffectRemoveFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript::OnDispel, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAPPLY);
2088 AfterEffectApply += AuraEffectApplyFn(spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript::AfterDispel, EFFECT_0, SPELL_AURA_PERIODIC_DAMAGE, AURA_EFFECT_HANDLE_REAPPLY);
2089 }
2090
2091 int32 _lastAmount;
2092 };
2093
2094 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override
2095 {
2096 return new spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_SpellScript();
2097 }
2098
2099 AuraScript* GetAuraScript() const override
2100 {
2101 return new spell_the_lich_king_necrotic_plague_AuraScript();
2102 }

2200class npc_icc_ice_sphere : public CreatureScript
2201{
2202public:

2204
2205 struct npc_icc_ice_sphereAI : public ScriptedAI
2206 {
2207 npc_icc_ice_sphereAI(Creature* creature) : ScriptedAI(creature)
2208 {
2209 targetGUID.Clear();
2210 timer = 250;
2211 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
2212 }
2213
2214 ObjectGuid targetGUID;
2215 uint16 timer;
2216
2217 void DoAction(int32 a) override
2218 {
2219 if (a == -1)
2220 {
2221 me->RemoveAllAuras();
2222 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_ICE_BURST, true);
2223 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(1000);
2224 targetGUID.Clear();
2225 timer = 9999;
2226 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(true);
2227 me->AttackStop();
2228 me->GetMotionMaster()->Clear();
2229 me->StopMoving();
2230 }
2231 }
2232
2233 void SelectNewTarget()
2234 {
2235 if (!me->HasAura(SPELL_ICE_SPHERE))
2236 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_ICE_SPHERE, true);
2237 targetGUID.Clear();
2238 me->InterruptNonMeleeSpells(true);
2239 me->AttackStop();
2240 me->GetMotionMaster()->Clear();
2241 me->StopMoving();
2242 if (Player* p = ScriptedAI::SelectTargetFromPlayerList(120.0f, SPELL_ICE_PULSE, false))
2243 {
2244 targetGUID = p->GetGUID();
2245 me->CastSpell(p, SPELL_ICE_PULSE, false);
2246 me->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING);
2247 me->Attack(p, true);
2248 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFollow(p, 0.01f, 0.0f);
2249 }
2250 }
2251
2252 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
2253 {
2254 if (timer > diff)
2255 {
2256 timer -= diff;
2257 return;
2258 }
2259 timer = 1000;
2260
2261 if (!targetGUID || !me->GetVictim() || !me->IsNonMeleeSpellCast(false, false, true, false, true))
2262 SelectNewTarget();
2263 else
2264 {
2265 Unit* target = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, targetGUID);
2266 if (me->GetVictim()->GetGUID() != targetGUID || !target || !me->IsValidAttackTarget(target) || target->HasUnitFlag2(UNIT_FLAG2_FEIGN_DEATH) || target->GetExactDist2dSq(&CenterPosition) > 75.0f * 75.0f || target->GetPositionZ() < 830.0f || target->GetPositionZ() > 855.0f)
2267 SelectNewTarget();
2268 }
2269 }
2270 };

2273 {
2274 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_icc_ice_sphereAI>(creature);
2275 }

2320 _events.Reset();
2321 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_RAGING_SPIRIT_UNROOT, 3000);
2322 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_SHRIEK, urand(12000, 15000));
2323
2324 bool valid = false;
2325 me->CastSpell(me, SPELL_RAGING_SPIRIT_VISUAL, true);
2326 if (TempSummon* summon = me->ToTempSummon())
2327 if (Unit* summoner = summon->GetSummonerUnit())
2328 if (summoner->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && summoner->IsAlive() && !summoner->ToPlayer()->IsBeingTeleported() && summoner->FindMap() == me->GetMap())

2339 }

2346 lichKing->AI()->JustSummoned(me);

2356 summon->SetTempSummonType(TEMPSUMMON_TIMED_DESPAWN);

2363 ScriptedAI::AttackStart(who);

2370 _events.Update(diff);
2371

2373 return;

2376 {
2377 case EVENT_RAGING_SPIRIT_UNROOT:
2378 {
2379 me->SetControlled(false, UNIT_STATE_ROOT);
2380
2381 if (!me->GetThreatMgr().isThreatListEmpty())
2382 if (Unit* target = me->SelectVictim())

2384 if (!me->GetVictim())

2386 bool valid = false;
2387 if (TempSummon* summon = me->ToTempSummon())
2388 if (Unit* summoner = summon->GetSummonerUnit())
2389 if (summoner->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && summoner->IsAlive() && !summoner->ToPlayer()->IsBeingTeleported() && summoner->FindMap() == me->GetMap())

2391 valid = true;
2392 AttackStart(summoner);
2393 }
2394 if (!valid)
2395 if (Player* plr = ScriptedAI::SelectTargetFromPlayerList(100.0f, 0, true))
2396 AttackStart(plr);
2397 }
2398 DoZoneInCombat(nullptr, 150.0f);
2399 }
2400 break;
2401 case EVENT_SOUL_SHRIEK:
2402 if (!me->HasReactState(REACT_PASSIVE))
2403 me->CastSpell(me->GetVictim(), SPELL_SOUL_SHRIEK, false);
2404 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_SHRIEK, urand(12000, 15000));
2405 break;
2406 default:
2407 break;
2408 }
2409
2410 if (!me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ROOT))
2411 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
2412 }

2417 }

2511class npc_valkyr_shadowguard : public CreatureScript
2512{
2513public:
2514 npc_valkyr_shadowguard() : CreatureScript("npc_valkyr_shadowguard") { }
2515
2516 struct npc_valkyr_shadowguardAI : public NullCreatureAI
2517 {
2518 npc_valkyr_shadowguardAI(Creature* creature) : NullCreatureAI(creature), didbelow50pct(false), dropped(false), _instance(creature->GetInstanceScript())
2519 {
2520 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
2521 me->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_STATE, SPELL_AURA_MOD_TAUNT, true);
2522 me->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_EFFECT, SPELL_EFFECT_ATTACK_ME, true);
2523 _events.Reset();
2524 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_GRAB_PLAYER, 2500);
2525 me->SetWalk(false);
2526 }
2527
2528 EventMap _events;
2529 Position _destPoint;
2530 ObjectGuid _grabbedPlayer;
2531 bool didbelow50pct;
2532 bool dropped;
2533 InstanceScript* _instance;
2534
2535 bool IsHeroic() { return me->GetMap()->IsHeroic(); }
2536
2537 void GoSiphon()
2538 {
2539 didbelow50pct = true;
2540 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_EJECT_ALL_PASSENGERS, false);
2541 float dist = rand_norm() * 10.0f + 5.0f;
2542 float angle = CenterPosition.GetAngle(me);
2543 _destPoint.Relocate(CenterPosition.GetPositionX() + dist * cos(angle), CenterPosition.GetPositionY() + dist * std::sin(angle), 855.0f + frand(0.0f, 4.0f), 0.0f);
2544 me->SetHomePosition(_destPoint);
2545 _events.Reset();
2546 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MOVE_TO_SIPHON_POS, 0);
2547 }
2548
2549 void OnCharmed(bool /*apply*/) override {}
2550
2551 void PassengerBoarded(Unit* pass, int8 /*seat*/, bool apply) override
2552 {
2553 if (apply)
2554 {
2555 //pass->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ONVEHICLE);
2556 return;
2557 }
2558 pass->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(VEHICLE_SPELL_PARACHUTE);
2559 if (didbelow50pct || dropped)
2560 return;
2561 if (IsHeroic())
2562 GoSiphon();
2563 else
2564 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(1000);
2565 }
2566
2567 void DamageTaken(Unit*, uint32& damage, DamageEffectType, SpellSchoolMask) override
2568 {
2569 if (IsHeroic() && !didbelow50pct && !dropped && me->HealthBelowPctDamaged(50, damage))
2570 GoSiphon();
2571 }
2572
2573 void MovementInform(uint32 type, uint32 id) override
2574 {
2575 if (type != POINT_MOTION_TYPE)
2576 return;
2577
2578 switch (id)
2579 {
2580 case EVENT_CHARGE:
2581 {
2582 bool valid = false;
2583 if (Player* target = ObjectAccessor::GetPlayer(*me, _grabbedPlayer))
2584 if (target->FindMap() == me->GetMap() && target->GetExactDist(me) < 15.0f && !target->GetVehicle())
2585 if (GameObject* platform = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_ARTHAS_PLATFORM)))
2586 {
2587 std::list<Creature*> triggers;
2588 GetCreatureListWithEntryInGrid(triggers, me, NPC_WORLD_TRIGGER, 150.0f);
2589 triggers.remove_if(HeightDifferenceCheck(platform, 5.0f, true));
2590 if (!triggers.empty())
2591 {
2592 valid = true;
2593 triggers.sort(Acore::ObjectDistanceOrderPred(me));
2594
2595 target->GetMotionMaster()->Clear();
2596 target->UpdatePosition(*me, true);
2597 target->StopMovingOnCurrentPos();
2598
2599 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_VALKYR_CARRY, false);
2600 _destPoint.Relocate(triggers.front());
2601 _events.Reset();
2602 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MOVE_TO_DROP_POS, 1000);
2603 }
2604 }
2605 if (!valid)
2606 {
2607 _events.Reset();
2608 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_GRAB_PLAYER, 500);
2609 _grabbedPlayer.Clear();
2610 }
2611 }
2612 break;
2613 case POINT_DROP_PLAYER:
2614 {
2615 if (didbelow50pct || dropped)
2616 break;
2617 if (me->GetExactDist(&_destPoint) > 1.5f) // movement was interrupted (probably by a stun, start again)
2618 {
2619 _events.Reset();
2620 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MOVE_TO_DROP_POS, 0);
2621 break;
2622 }
2623 dropped = true;
2624 _events.Reset();
2625 /*Player* p = nullptr;
2626 if (Vehicle* v = me->GetVehicleKit())
2627 if (Unit* passenger = v->GetPassenger(0))
2628 p = passenger->ToPlayer();*/
2629 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_EJECT_ALL_PASSENGERS, false);
2630
2631 if (IsHeroic())
2632 GoSiphon();
2633 else
2634 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(1000);
2635 }
2636 break;
2637 case POINT_START_SIPHON:
2638 if (me->GetExactDist(&_destPoint) > 1.5f) // movement was interrupted (probably by a stun, start again)
2639 {
2640 _events.Reset();
2641 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MOVE_TO_SIPHON_POS, 0);
2642 break;
2643 }
2644 me->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_STATE, SPELL_AURA_MOD_TAUNT, false);
2645 me->ApplySpellImmune(0, IMMUNITY_EFFECT, SPELL_EFFECT_ATTACK_ME, false);
2646 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LIFE_SIPHON, 2000);
2647 break;
2648 }
2649 }
2650
2651 void SetGUID(ObjectGuid guid, int32 /* = 0*/) override
2652 {
2653 _grabbedPlayer = guid;
2654 }
2655
2656 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
2657 {
2658 _events.Update(diff);
2659
2660 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING | UNIT_STATE_STUNNED))
2661 return;
2662
2663 switch (_events.ExecuteEvent())
2664 {
2665 case EVENT_GRAB_PLAYER:
2666 if (!_grabbedPlayer)
2667 {
2668 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_VALKYR_TARGET_SEARCH, false);
2669 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_GRAB_PLAYER, 2000);
2670 }
2671 break;
2672 case EVENT_MOVE_TO_DROP_POS:
2673 me->AddUnitState(UNIT_STATE_NO_ENVIRONMENT_UPD);
2674 me->SetCanFly(false);
2675 me->SetDisableGravity(false);
2676 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_DROP_PLAYER, _destPoint, false);
2677 me->SetDisableGravity(true, true);
2678 me->RemoveUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE);
2679 break;
2680 case EVENT_MOVE_TO_SIPHON_POS:
2681 me->RemoveUnitFlag(UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE); // just in case if passenger disappears so quickly that EVENT_MOVE_TO_DROP_POS is never executed
2682 { int32 bp0 = 80; me->CastCustomSpell(me, 1557, &bp0, nullptr, nullptr, true); }
2683 me->SetCanFly(true);
2684 me->SetDisableGravity(true);
2685 me->SendMovementFlagUpdate();
2686 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_START_SIPHON, _destPoint);
2687 break;
2688 case EVENT_LIFE_SIPHON:
2689 {
2690 Unit* target = nullptr;
2691 Unit::AuraEffectList const& tauntAuras = me->GetAuraEffectsByType(SPELL_AURA_MOD_TAUNT);
2692 if (!tauntAuras.empty())
2693 for (Unit::AuraEffectList::const_reverse_iterator itr = tauntAuras.rbegin(); itr != tauntAuras.rend(); ++itr)
2694 if (Unit* caster = (*itr)->GetCaster())
2695 if (me->IsValidAttackTarget(caster))
2696 {
2697 target = caster;
2698 break;
2699 }
2700 if (!target)
2701 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
2702 target = lichKing->AI()->SelectTarget(SelectTargetMethod::Random, 0, NonTankLKTargetSelector(lichKing, true, false, 100.0f));
2703 if (target)
2704 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_LIFE_SIPHON, false);
2705 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LIFE_SIPHON, 2500);
2706 }
2707 break;
2708 default:
2709 break;
2710 }
2711 }
2712 };
2713
2714 CreatureAI* GetAI(Creature* creature) const override
2715 {
2716 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_valkyr_shadowguardAI>(creature);

2793class spell_the_lich_king_valkyr_target_search : public SpellScriptLoader

2797
2798 class spell_the_lich_king_valkyr_target_search_SpellScript : public SpellScript
2799 {
2800 PrepareSpellScript(spell_the_lich_king_valkyr_target_search_SpellScript);
2801
2802 WorldObject* _target;
2803
2804 bool Load() override
2805 {
2806 _target = nullptr;
2807 return true;
2808 }
2809
2810 void SelectTarget(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
2811 {
2812 if (targets.empty())
2813 return;
2814 Creature* caster = GetCaster()->ToCreature();
2815 if (!caster)
2816 {
2817 targets.clear();
2818 return;
2819 }
2820 targets.remove_if(Acore::UnitAuraCheck(true, GetSpellInfo()->Id));
2821 targets.remove_if(Acore::UnitAuraCheck(true, SPELL_BOSS_HITTIN_YA_AURA)); // done in dbc, but just to be sure xd
2822 targets.remove_if(Acore::UnitAuraCheck(true, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_VALKYR));
2823 if (InstanceScript* _instance = caster->GetInstanceScript())
2824 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*caster, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
2825 if (Spell* s = lichKing->GetCurrentSpell(CURRENT_GENERIC_SPELL))
2826 if (s->GetSpellInfo()->Id == SPELL_DEFILE && s->m_targets.GetUnitTarget())
2827 targets.remove(s->m_targets.GetUnitTarget());
2828
2829 if (targets.empty())
2830 return;
2831
2832 _target = Acore::Containers::SelectRandomContainerElement(targets);
2833 targets.clear();
2834 targets.push_back(_target);
2835 if (Creature* caster = GetCaster()->ToCreature())
2836 caster->AI()->SetGUID(_target->GetGUID());
2837 }
2838
2839 void ReplaceTarget(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
2840 {
2841 targets.clear();
2842 if (_target)
2843 targets.push_back(_target);
2844 }
2845
2846 void HandleScript(SpellEffIndex effIndex)
2847 {
2848 PreventHitDefaultEffect(effIndex);
2849 if (Unit* target = GetHitUnit())
2850 {
2851 GetCaster()->GetMotionMaster()->MoveCharge(target->GetPositionX(), target->GetPositionY(), target->GetPositionZ() + 4.0f, 42.0f, EVENT_CHARGE);
2852 GetCaster()->SetDisableGravity(true, true);
2853 }
2854 }
2855
2856 void Register() override
2857 {
2858 OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_the_lich_king_valkyr_target_search_SpellScript::SelectTarget, EFFECT_0, TARGET_UNIT_SRC_AREA_ENEMY);
2859 OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_the_lich_king_valkyr_target_search_SpellScript::ReplaceTarget, EFFECT_1, TARGET_UNIT_SRC_AREA_ENEMY);
2860 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_the_lich_king_valkyr_target_search_SpellScript::HandleScript, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_SCRIPT_EFFECT);
2861 }
2862 };

3121 EventMap _events;

3123
3124 void IsSummonedBy(Unit* summoner) override
3125 {
3126 if (!summoner)
3127 return;
3128
3129 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
3130 {
3131 me->SetWalk(false);
3132 Movement::PointsArray path;
3133 path.push_back(G3D::Vector3(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), me->GetPositionZ()));
3134 path.push_back(G3D::Vector3(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), 843.0f));
3135 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveSplinePath(&path);
3136
3137 ObjectGuid petGUID = summoner->GetPetGUID();
3138 summoner->SetPetGUID(ObjectGuid::Empty);
3139 summoner->StopMoving();
3140 me->CastSpell(summoner, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_VEHICLE, true);
3141 //summoner->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_ONVEHICLE);
3142 summoner->SendMovementFlagUpdate(true);
3143 summoner->SetPetGUID(petGUID);
3144 _events.Reset();
3145 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_MOVE_TO_LICH_KING, 1000);
3146 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TELEPORT, 6250);
3147 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DESPAWN_SELF, 6000 + 70000);
3148
3149 // this will let us easily access all creatures of this entry on heroic mode when its time to teleport back
3150 lichKing->AI()->JustSummoned(me);
3151 }
3152 }
3153
3154 bool IsHeroic() { return me->GetMap()->IsHeroic(); }
3155 void OnCharmed(bool /*apply*/) override {}
3156 void PassengerBoarded(Unit* pass, int8 /*seat*/, bool apply) override
3157 {
3158 if (!apply)
3159 pass->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(VEHICLE_SPELL_PARACHUTE);
3160 }
3161
3162 void DoAction(int32 action) override
3163 {
3164 if (action != ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK)
3165 return;
3166
3167 if (TempSummon* summ = me->ToTempSummon())
3168 {
3169 if (Unit* summoner = summ->GetSummonerUnit())
3170 {
3171 bool buff = _instance->GetBossState(DATA_THE_LICH_KING) == IN_PROGRESS && summoner->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && (!summoner->IsAlive() || summoner->ToPlayer()->IsBeingTeleported() || summoner->FindMap() != me->GetMap());
3172 if (summoner->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && !summoner->ToPlayer()->IsBeingTeleported() && summoner->FindMap() == me->GetMap())
3173 {
3174 if (buff)
3175 summoner->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_HARVESTED_SOUL_LK_BUFF, true, nullptr, nullptr, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING));
3176
3177 me->CastSpell(summoner, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_TELEPORT_BACK, false);
3178 }
3179 else if (buff)
3180 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_HARVESTED_SOUL_LK_BUFF, true, nullptr, nullptr, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING));
3181
3182 summoner->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(IsHeroic() ? SPELL_HARVEST_SOULS_TELEPORT : SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_TELEPORT);
3183 }
3184 else
3185 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_HARVESTED_SOUL_LK_BUFF, true, nullptr, nullptr, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING));
3186 }
3187
3188 _events.Reset();
3189 me->RemoveAllAuras();
3190 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(500);
3191
3192 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
3193 lichKing->AI()->SummonedCreatureDespawn(me);
3194 }
3195
3196 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
3197 {
3198 _events.Update(diff);
3199
3200 switch (_events.ExecuteEvent())
3201 {
3202 case EVENT_TELEPORT:
3203 me->GetMotionMaster()->Clear(false);
3204 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveIdle();
3205 if (TempSummon* summ = me->ToTempSummon())
3206 if (Unit* summoner = summ->GetSummonerUnit())
3207 {
3208 if (summoner->IsAlive() && summoner->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER)
3209 {
3210 summoner->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_VISUAL, true);
3211 summoner->ExitVehicle(summoner);
3212 me->UpdatePosition(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), 840.87f, me->GetOrientation(), true);
3213 me->StopMovingOnCurrentPos();
3214 if (!IsHeroic())
3215 summoner->CastSpell(summoner, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_TELEPORT, true);
3216 else
3217 summoner->CastSpell(summoner, SPELL_HARVEST_SOULS_TELEPORT, true);
3218 }
3219 else
3220 {
3221 summoner->ExitVehicle(summoner);
3222 _events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_DESPAWN_SELF, 0);
3223 }
3224 }
3225 break;
3226 case EVENT_MOVE_TO_LICH_KING:
3227 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
3228 if (me->GetExactDist(lichKing) > 8.0f)
3229 {
3230 float dist = float(rand_norm()) * 5.0f + 8.0f;
3231 float angle = lichKing->GetAngle(me);
3232 Movement::PointsArray path;
3233 path.push_back(G3D::Vector3(me->GetPositionX(), me->GetPositionY(), me->GetPositionZ()));
3234 path.push_back(G3D::Vector3(lichKing->GetPositionX() + dist * cos(angle), lichKing->GetPositionY() + dist * std::sin(angle), 843.0f));
3235 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveSplinePath(&path);
3236 }
3237 break;
3238 case EVENT_DESPAWN_SELF:
3239 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
3240 lichKing->AI()->SummonedCreatureDespawn(me);
3241 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(1);
3242 break;
3243 default:
3244 break;
3245 }
3246 }
3247 };

3250 {
3251 return GetIcecrownCitadelAI<npc_strangulate_vehicleAI>(creature);
3252 }

3400 void CalculateBonus(AuraEffect const* /*aurEff*/, int32& amount, bool& canBeRecalculated)

3650 timer = 0;

3656 {

3659 destZ = 1055.0f; // approximation, gets more precise later

3662 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_GROUND, destX, destY, destZ);
3663 }

3666 {
3667 if (type != POINT_MOTION_TYPE || point != POINT_GROUND)
3668 return;
3669
3670 timer = 1000;
3671 }

3674 {
3675 if (timer)
3676 {
3677 if (timer <= diff)
3678 {
3679 timer = 0;
3680 me->RemoveAllAuras();
3681 me->CastSpell((Unit*)nullptr, SPELL_EXPLOSION, false);
3682 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(1000);
3683 }
3684 else
3685 timer -= diff;
3686 }
3687 }
